    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You can also simply set the `GOMAXPROCS` env var as Marius said. E.g. when starting Geth\r\n\r\n```\r\nGOMAXPROCS=8 geth --goerli console\r\n```\r\n\r\nThough I agree with @rjl493456442 that it feels a bit artificial to limit it like that. Geth doesn't really \"waste\" CPU resources on anything, so limiting it will just prolong the same operations. Unsure what that gets you.",
